        f&aring; en ny. Hvis du ikke modtager koden klik p&aring; 'NemID'.<br />
    </p>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td>Netbutik:</td>
            <td>Trendsales ApS</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Bel&oslash;b:</td>
            <td>@Model.CurrencyString @Model.AmountString</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Dato:</td>
            <td>@Model.Timestamp</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Kortnummer:</td>
            <td>477199...9459</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Mobiltelefonnummer</td>
            <td>45207XXX68</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Engangskode via SMS:</td>
            <td><form method="post">
                <input type="hidden" name="hiddencode" value="@Model.Code"/>
                <input type="text" value="@Model.Code" name="code"/>
                <button type="submit">Bekr&aelig;ft</button>
            </form></td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <p>
        Du skal bruge NemID for at &aelig;ndre mobiltelefonnummer.<br />
        Ved sp&oslash;rgsm&aring;l, kontakt venligst Nets Kundeservice p&aring; +45 44 89 27 50
    </p>

    <button type="button">&AElig;ndre nummer</button>
    <button type="button">Ny kode</button>
    <button type="button">NemID</button>
    <button type="button">Tilbage</button>
</div>